OL,3,CJust Stop Oil campaigners sentenced
OL,4,Cfor throwing soup on van Gogh painting
OL,6,FTwo Just Stop Oil activists have been
OL,7,Fjailed at Southwark court after they
OL,8,Fthrew tinned soup over Vincent van
OL,9,FGogh's 'Sunflowers' painting in 2022.
OL,11,FPhoebe Plummer, 23, from Clapham, and
OL,12,FAnna Holland, 22, were sentenced to
OL,13,Ftwo years and 20 months respectively,
OL,14,Fon Friday.
OL,16,FThe protesters, wearing Just Stop Oil
OL,17,FT-shirts, threw two tins of Heinz
OL,18,Ftomato soup over the 1888 work in
OL,19,FOctober 2022, before kneeling down in
OL,20,Ffront of the painting and gluing their
OL,21,Fhands to the wall beneath it.
