OL,3,CJust Stop Oil campaigners sentenced
OL,4,Cfor throwing soup on van Gogh painting
OL,6,FThe painting was not damaged due to
OL,7,Fbeing behind glass, however the frame
OL,8,Fsuffered #10,000 worth of damage, the
OL,9,Fcourt heard.
OL,11,FThe pair were found guilty of criminal
OL,12,Fdamage in July 2024. Judge Christopher
OL,13,FHehir had warned the pair to be
OL,14,F'prepared in practical and emotional
OL,15,Fterms to go to prison.'
OL,17,FSentencing the women on Friday, Judge
OL,18,FChristopher Hehir said the "cultural
OL,19,Ftreasure" could have been "seriously
OL,20,Fdamaged or even destroyed".
