OL,3,CJust Stop Oil campaigners sentenced
OL,4,Cfor throwing soup on van Gogh painting
OL,6,F"Soup might have seeped through the
OL,7,Fglass," he continued.
OL,9,F"You couldn't have cared less if the
OL,10,Fpainting was damaged or not. You had
OL,11,Fno right to do what you did to
OL,12,FSunflowers."
OL,14,FThe judge told Plummer, who was also
OL,15,Fhanded a criminal behaviour order:
OL,16,F"You clearly think your beliefs give
OL,17,Fyou the right to commit crimes when
OL,18,Fyou feel like it. You do not."
