OL,3,CJust Stop Oil campaigners sentenced
OL,4,Cfor throwing soup on van Gogh painting
OL,6,FRaj Chada, defending Holland, said the
OL,7,Fwomen "did check" that the painting
OL,8,Fwas protected by a glass cover before
OL,9,Fthrowing the soup.
OL,11,FPlummer, representing herself, told
OL,12,Fthe hearing: "My choice today is to
OL,13,Faccept whatever sentence I receive
OL,14,Fwith a smile.
OL,16,F"It is not just myself being sentenced
OL,17,Ftoday, or my co-defendants, but the
OL,18,Ffoundations of democracy itself."
