OL,3,CJust Stop Oil campaigners sentenced
OL,4,Cfor throwing soup on van Gogh painting
OL,6,FPlummer was also handed a three-month
OL,7,Fsentence for her part in a slow march
OL,8,Fwhich caused long tailbacks in west
OL,9,FLondon in November 2023.
OL,11,FA number of Just Stop Oil supporters
OL,12,Fgathered outside the court, some of
OL,13,Fwhom held posters of historical
OL,14,Ffigures jailed for activism. One sign
OL,15,Fread, "Free Political Prisoners."
